Panner by Nandhini--

Now i will tell you how to make panner yourself

Take one milk packet 
put it in vessel and boil it
once it starts to boil, put the gas in sim
Now put some lemon juice in the boiling milk and mix it well until the curd and the water gets seperated
switch off the stove
now put the curd in some cloth and squeeze it to take away all water, wash the curd with cool water 2/3 times
then, cover the curd with the same cloth and keep that under some weight.
After 2 to 3 hours take the panner and cut it into pieces and use it for your dishes
